sequenceDiagram
    participant ROM as ROM Code
    participant SD as SD Card
    participant SPL as SPL (SRAM)
    participant DDR as DDR3
    participant KRNS as _start
    participant KRNC as kmain

    ROM ->>+ SD: Read MLO (sector 0)
    SD -->>- ROM: 109 KB binary
    ROM ->> SPL: Copy to SRAM 0x402F0400, jump

    activate SPL
    Note over SPL: mask IRQ, setup stacks, disable WDT1

    SPL ->>+ DDR: clock_init() + ddr_init()
    DDR -->>- SPL: 512 MB DDR3 ready

    SPL ->>+ SD: mmc_read_sectors(2048, 2048)
    SD ->> DDR: kernel.bin to 0x80000000
    SD -->>- SPL: ok

    Note over SPL, KRNS: r0=0, r1=0x0E05, r2=0<br/>ldr pc, =0x80000000
    SPL ->> KRNS: jump (no return)
    deactivate SPL

    activate KRNS
    KRNS ->> KRNS: cpsid if
    
    loop 5 exception modes
        KRNS ->> KRNS: cps [mode], ldr sp =stack_top
    end
    
    KRNS ->> KRNS: zero BSS
    KRNS ->>+ KRNC: bl kmain
    deactivate KRNS

    KRNC ->> KRNC: uart_init() NS16550
    KRNC ->> KRNC: uart_puts("Boot OK")
    Note over KRNC: for(&#59;&#59;) halt